<paragraph blockId="32.[151,684,1413,1666]" pageId="32" pageNumber="91">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="91">
Plantae 10-15(-20) cm altae, cormo depresso-campanulato 
<quantity box="[221,327,1438,1462]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.75" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="17.5" valueMax="20.0" valueMin="15.0">15-20 mm</quantity>
diam., foliis 3 ad 5, filiformibus in sectione transversali ovalibus 4-sulcatis, 
<quantity box="[521,616,1464,1488]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="1.6" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.2">1.2-2 mm</quantity>
diam., inflorescentiae bracteis exterioribus 
<quantity box="[505,613,1489,1513]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" metricValueMax="2.8" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="21.5" valueMax="28.0" valueMin="15.0">15-28 mm</quantity>
longis, interioribus marginibus anguste membranaceis basem versus dilatatis, floribus flavis brunneonotatis prope basem tepalorum internorum, tubo perianthii infundibuliformi c. 
<quantity box="[249,307,1591,1614]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
longo, tepalis 25-35
</emphasis>
× 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="91">
<quantity box="[539,634,1591,1616]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="6.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="8.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="6.0">6-10 mm</quantity>
, laxe patentibus, filamentis 
<quantity box="[375,457,1616,1641]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5-6 mm</quantity>
longis, antheris erectis contiguis 
<quantity box="[239,316,1642,1666]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.5" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="6.0" pageId="32" pageNumber="91" unit="mm" value="6.5" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="6.0">6-7 mm</quantity>
longis.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
